      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/1/13/2",
      "text": [
        ": كتاب الله فيه نبأ ما قبلكم وخبر ما بعدكم وفصل ما بينكم ونحن نعلمه"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "2. [2/65] al-Kafi: A number of our companions from Ahmad b. Muhammad b. Isa from Ali b. al-Nu’man from Ismail b. Jabir from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام who said: the book of Allāh – in it is an account of what came before you and a report of what will come after you and a judgment of what is between you (of differences) – and we do know it (all)."
        ]
      }
    },
